Windlord picked up him and carried him towards cr's where, the hawk 
left him in one. Nightlight saw him and yelled with sorrow "Aerotaur, 
Aerotaur.. are you ok? you will survive... You can't die... TRinity 
need you..."

But she didn't say that, she needed him too.. Windlord closed cr's 
door and walked where Nightlight was.
